<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-363] NPE when recovering ledger with no hint </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-363</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When recovering a ledger, LedgerRecoveryMonitor currently start from the entry preceding the hint. if the hint is zero, then it causes an access out of the bounds of the bookie array in QuorumEngine, leading to the mentioned NPE.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
